Pineapple Salsa
  --Cook's Country

2 c (12 oz) 1+ pineapple pieces (not canned)
3 jalapeno chiles, stemmed,seeded, and cut into 1/2" pieces
1 c fresh cilantro leaves
1/4 c coarsely chopped red onion
2 garlic cloves, peeled and smashed
1 tbsp fresh lime juice
1 tbsp evoo
1/2 tsp salt
1/2 tsp pepper

Pulse pineapple, jalape√±os, cilantro, onion, and garlic in food processor until coarsely chopped, ~6 pulses, scraping down sides of bowl as needed. Transfer to serving bowl. Stir in lime juice, oil, salt, and pepper. Serve.

Note: For spicier salsa, use the jalapeno seeds
